<item>
            <title>[SPARK-18637] Stateful UDF should be considered as nondeterministic</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-18637</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the annotation UDFType of a udf is stateful, it shoudl be considered as non-deterministic. Otherwise, the catalyst may optimize the plan and return the wrong result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13024250">SPARK-18637</key>
            <summary>Stateful UDF should be considered as nondeterministic</summary>
